NAME
  aspectsnes - adjusts image files in the current directory to the aspect ratio that the SNES appears on a CRT television
SYNOPSIS
  aspectsnes
DESCRIPTION
  aspectsnes converts every image file of a variety of formats 
  (tga, bmp, png, gif, jpeg)
  in the current working directory to a 620x480 png
  image.
  Conversion is performed using ImageMagick(1)'s convert(1) utility.
  The output files are placed into a 'out' subfolder, 
  which is created if needed.
SEE ALSO
  ImageMagick(1), convert(1)
AUTHOR
  Ryan Armstrong <software@zerker.ca>
